author: David Cuello
description:
Full-page OCR for 200+ languages.
 Based on ABBYY’s industry leading FineReader OCR technology, Cloud OCR SDK supports the recognition of printed text in more than 200 languages, including most Asian languages: Chinese, Japanese, Korean, Arabic, Farsi, Vietnamese, Thai and others.
